                  </persName>
             being questioned, appeared not to understand the nature of an oath, and was not examined.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was coming along, and an old lady asked me to run after the thief; he dropped the bundle, and they took me.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18220703-101-verdict526" type="verdictDescription">
